recipesJson.name: Stachio custard cookie
recipesJson.author: NastyNate
recipesJson.description: Stachio Custard Cookie. Idea came from psiquid eliquids “bosphorus”. They don't have sugar cookie in it, but I freaking love Cap sugar cookie so it was only necessary! Enjoy friends!

reviews.text: I’m a custard/Sugar cookie freak. This is really good. Thanks
